MTN “Mega Deals” which form part of its Black Friday 2018 promotion are available on Cyber Monday. The Mega Deals promotion is valid until 26 November 2018, with specials on data deals and smartphone contracts – including My MTNChoice data contracts that provide both anytime and Night Express data. What’s more is that customers who sign up or upgrade during the sale will also receive a 12-month MTN Entertainment Pass. The MTN Entertainment Pass gives customers on selected price plans Facebook, WhatsApp, Twitter, YouTube, Deezer, Simfy Africa, DStv Now, and ShowMax data for free. Additionally, customers will receive 20GB of free anytime data – once-off – valid for 30 days, when signing up for a My MTNChoice data plan. A selection of MTN’s Cyber Monday 2018 deals are listed below.   